    edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.Model

    public class Attachment
extends edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.AbstractModel
    A class used contain files, along with their names and a reference to the Requirement that they are attached to. the contents are Base64 encoded.
